data.text:
@AuschwitzMuseum (1/n) Betty was the daughter of Maurits, born 21-04-1910 and Bertha nee de Leeuw, born 31-08-1911.
Betty had a younger brother Simon, born 13-04-1939.
The family lived in Amsterdam.
The family has been in hiding but it's unclear (to me) where the parents were in hiding.
⬇️ https://t.co/Vsj4l2GLea
